2020-04-11T13:15:11.000Z","msg":"中國抗議安倍晉三轉發蔡英文帖文2020/04/11 20:58<br />\n【有線新聞】日本傳媒報道，中國向日本提出抗議，不滿首相安倍晉三感謝蔡英文。<br />\n<br />\n安倍晉三早前在Twitter轉載蔡英文的帖文，內容提到台灣願意與日方攜手抗疫，安倍晉三又以日文和中文向台方致謝，並稱「日本台灣一起加油」。《讀賣新聞》引述政府消息報道，中國外交部認為安倍的帖文有問題，已經透過外交渠道，向日本駐華大使館抗議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/22768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F22768&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W8wxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=b277899d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F22768&h=d26341f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/22768</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:13:51.000Z","msg":"連講多謝都唔比咁撚惡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d95a3a8243150d6b1486c8f3a92632e884ee08","tid":1968200,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:14:26.000Z","msg":"Abe: DLLMCH，唔比出口口罩去支那"},{"pid":"cec7f6fa81247c9071f505e6d6d844029aceab91","tid":1968200,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:15:25.000Z","msg":"無左台灣海峽 日本即死<br />\n無左支那 仲大把東南亞客去日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4e3319a366927629cf3630ec0b4e207fa50401","tid":1968200,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:15:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"87d22a35b4b3495b887bc0613f5470d9a1ba2823","tid":1968200,"uid":333631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:17:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好樣衰啊"},{"pid":"02558c7c57c2fcc011b738a334f21571005c28e0","tid":1968200,"uid":254769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"